<B>Steps to duplicate:</B><BR>
<INPUT TYPE="hidden"  NAME="steps" VAlUE="Attack a group of war magic casting monsters. Make sure one is directly behind another one in relation to you. Hopefully the 2 monsters will both choose to cast spells. If the monster behind casts a war spell and the spell hits the one in front the graphics stop coming toward you. BUT, the spell effect is still traveling even though the graphics have stopped. If you don't move the spell will hit you.">
Attack a group of war magic casting monsters. Make sure one is directly behind another one in relation to you. Hopefully the 2 monsters will both choose to cast spells. If the monster behind casts a war spell and the spell hits the one in front the graphics stop coming toward you. BUT, the spell effect is still traveling even though the graphics have stopped. If you don't move the spell will hit you.
